{"tid":1078973,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【好正呀】呂麗瑤Deep V到場 搶盡全場目光","createTime":"2019-03-26T15:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T02:00:58.000Z","uid":37358,"like":21,"dislike":1601,"uniUserReply":140,"replies":[{"pid":"e307fbe4de734e589324dbd258b08400e2c3262f","tid":1078973,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59415347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59415347&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=4f65831d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59415347&h=ce1a3939\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59415347</a><br />\n<br />\n香港體壇奧斯卡的香港傑出運動員頒獎禮，今晚在會展舉行，六時展開的紅地氈，運動員都盛裝出席，有不少驚喜，特別是「欄后」呂麗瑤及滑浪風帆的馬君正，集合性感、型格，搶了不少鎂光燈。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的「呂神」闊別傑運頒獎禮六年，她笑說六年前是穿着運動服出席頒獎禮，今次難得大會講明要「盛裝」，就選了這套性感得來又型格的衣服，她說服裝是上網買的：「六年前好後悔着了田總的運動服來，今日三點半就去了整頭，然後回家換衫，今次選這套是知道自己身型不適合露膊，會顯得好大隻，這件可遮到膊頭及手臂，亦顯得很elegant。」呂麗瑤原本今日要隨隊到新加坡比賽，但為了出席頒獎禮，明日才自己飛去新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1iq51G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1iq51G.jpg&h=9acf7a29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b067efa456f59085d07bed0d8c5d9204a73d1abe","tid":1078973,"uid":184116,"like":25,"dislike":112,"score":-87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bcfea165db63d117401dc8b0ad6087927e67d1","tid":1078973,"uid":35014,"like":906,"dislike":4,"score":902,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:20:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4c6acbbf9d9b80695b381bcf46162efc5ffe5b6","tid":10789